title: Hidden Messages in Sound - The Farside Paranormal Podcast Episod
description:
Are there secret messages residing inside everyday, verbal communication? 

Brian Jones is an audio-psychic medium. 
One who has conducted 16 1/2 years of research and experimentation into an unusual phenomenon called energy signals or psychic information.

This is episode #5 of The new Paranormal Podcast called "The Farside".
Episode #5 is just over 2 hours.
Give it a listen.

The host is new to podcasting but he's doing a decent job; he should get better with time.
